---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Custom Electronics Services - From Concept to Prototype"
  description="Complete electronics development services: circuit design, PCB fabrication, firmware development, 3D printing, and system integration. Turn your ideas into working devices."
  keywords="electronics services, PCB design, firmware development, prototype development, IoT consulting, embedded systems">

<section class="services-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>From Concept to Working Prototype</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Complete electronics development services for your unique requirements</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services-overview">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="overview-grid">
      <div class="overview-content">
        <h2>What I Do</h2>
        <p>I design and build electronic devices for specific problems where standard products don't work or don't exist. Most projects involve monitoring something remotely, automating a process, or getting alerts when something needs attention.</p>
        <p>I work on <strong>one-off solutions</strong> - if you need hundreds of units, there are better options. But if you have a unique situation that needs a custom device, that's exactly what I do.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="overview-stats">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">25+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Years Experience</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Projects Delivered</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">15+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Industries Served</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services-detailed">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Service Areas</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
      
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">ðŸ”¬</div>
        <h3>Concept Development</h3>
        <p>Transform your ideas into viable technical solutions. I'll analyze your requirements, research existing solutions, and propose the best approach for your specific needs.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Requirements analysis and specification</li>
          <li>Technology selection and feasibility studies</li>
          <li>System architecture design</li>
          <li>Cost estimation and project planning</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">âš¡</div>
        <h3>Circuit Design & PCB Layout</h3>
        <p>Custom circuit design optimized for your application. From simple sensor interfaces to complex multi-layer PCBs with advanced functionality.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Analog and digital circuit design</li>
          <li>Power management and battery optimization</li>
          <li>Multi-layer PCB layout and routing</li>
          <li>Component selection and sourcing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">ðŸ’»</div>
        <h3>Firmware Development</h3>
        <p>Embedded software that brings your hardware to life. Efficient, reliable code optimized for your specific microcontroller and application requirements.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Microcontroller programming (STM32, ESP32, etc.)</li>
          <li>Real-time operating systems (FreeRTOS)</li>
          <li>Communication protocols (UART, SPI, I2C, CAN)</li>
          <li>Power optimization and sleep modes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">ðŸ“¡</div>
        <h3>Wireless & IoT Integration</h3>
        <p>Connect your devices to the world with reliable wireless communication. Expertise in multiple protocols and cloud integration platforms.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>LoRaWAN long-range communication</li>
          <li>WiFi and Bluetooth connectivity</li>
          <li>Cloud platform integration</li>
          <li>Mobile app development</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">ðŸ”§</div>
        <h3>Mechanical Design</h3>
        <p>Complete enclosure solutions using 3D printing and traditional manufacturing. Designed for your environment and aesthetic requirements.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>3D modeling and CAD design</li>
          <li>3D printing and rapid prototyping</li>
          <li>Weather-resistant enclosures</li>
          <li>Mounting hardware and fixtures</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">ðŸ§ª</div>
        <h3>Testing & Validation</h3>
        <p>Thorough testing ensures your device works reliably in real-world conditions. Comprehensive validation before deployment.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Functional and performance testing</li>
          <li>Environmental testing (temperature, humidity)</li>
          <li>EMC compliance assessment</li>
          <li>Long-term reliability evaluation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="process-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Development Process</h2>
    <div class="process-timeline">
      
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Discovery & Requirements</h3>
          <p>We start with a detailed discussion of your needs, constraints, and goals. I'll ask lots of questions to fully understand what you're trying to achieve.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Concept & Proposal</h3>
          <p>Based on our discussions, I'll develop a technical approach and provide a detailed proposal including timeline, costs, and deliverables.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Design & Development</h3>
          <p>I'll design the circuits, develop the firmware, and create the mechanical components. You'll receive regular updates on progress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Prototype & Testing</h3>
          <p>Build and test the first prototype, making any necessary adjustments. This iterative process ensures the final device meets your requirements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">5</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Delivery & Support</h3>
          <p>Deliver the completed device with documentation, installation support, and ongoing technical assistance as needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pricing-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Investment & Pricing</h2>
    <div class="pricing-content">
      <div class="pricing-text">
        <p>Every project is unique, so pricing varies based on complexity, timeline, and specific requirements. Here's how I approach pricing:</p>
        
        <div class="pricing-factors">
          <h3>Factors Affecting Cost:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Project complexity</strong> - Simple sensors vs. complex multi-function devices</li>
            <li><strong>Development time</strong> - Rush projects may incur premium pricing</li>
            <li><strong>Component costs</strong> - Specialized sensors or processors</li>
            <li><strong>Quantity</strong> - Single prototype vs. small production run</li>
            <li><strong>Testing requirements</strong> - Basic validation vs. comprehensive testing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-approach">
          <h3>My Approach:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Fixed price quotes</strong> - No surprises, you know the cost upfront</li>
            <li><strong>Milestone-based payments</strong> - Pay as progress is made</li>
            <li><strong>Transparent pricing</strong> - Detailed breakdown of costs</li>
            <li><strong>Value-focused</strong> - Competitive rates for high-quality work</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pricing-ranges">
        <h3>Typical Project Ranges:</h3>
        <div class="price-examples">
          <div class="price-item">
            <h4>Simple Sensor System</h4>
            <span class="price">$2,000 - $5,000</span>
            <p>Basic monitoring with wireless connectivity</p>
          </div>
          <div class="price-item">
            <h4>IoT Device with App</h4>
            <span class="price">$5,000 - $15,000</span>
            <p>Complex functionality, cloud integration, mobile app</p>
          </div>
          <div class="price-item">
            <h4>Industrial Automation</h4>
            <span class="price">$10,000 - $30,000</span>
            <p>Multi-sensor systems, control interfaces, safety systems</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="pricing-note">*Prices are estimates only. Each project is quoted individually based on specific requirements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>Ready to Start Your Project?</h2>
      <p>Let's discuss your requirements and see how I can help bring your ideas to life.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Start a Conversation</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="btn-secondary">View Past Projects</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
